*Kontrolom* je utvrđeno da nema nikakvih nepravilnosti. (It was established by control that there are no irregularities.)

*Kontrolom* je proveravana verodostojnost podataka. (The reliability of the data was checked by control.)

Kroz *kontrolu* je došlo do otkrivanja lažnih informacija. (False information was discovered through control.)

Nadležno lice je obavilo *kontrolu* na licu mesta. (The competent authority carried out the control on the spot.)

*Kontrolom* se proverava kvalitet rada. (The quality of the work is checked by control.)